author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Tony Iommi has been speaking about working with Robbie Williams on "Rocket" - the first single from Robbie's upcoming album,  "Britpop." Tony Iommi is a legend and I'll always be grateful to Robbie for reasons I explain in this episode.....

The full track is here: https://youtu.be/YfAFBOECxw4?si=xm25Ki4lG-WOPuZj

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk
